      "2_1_oxalic_acid_in_sugar_syrup_dribble": "2.1% oxalic acid in sugar syrup, dribbled between frames. Organic acid; kills phoretic mites on contact.",
      "most_effective_in_winter_when_there_s_": "Most effective in WINTER when there's no capped brood. If brood > 2,000, ~60% of mites are hiding in cells and untouchable — wait for a brood break. Legal organic treatment; leaves no residue in wax.",
      "formic_acid_pads": "Formic Acid Pads",
