      "you_re_managing_a_honeybee_colony_a_su": "You're managing a honeybee colony — a superorganism of 10,000 workers, a queen, and hundreds of drones. Your goal: keep the colony alive and thriving through all four seasons.",
      "advance_days": "Advance Days",
